room_title: Escape room "Alien Abduction" by Xtreme Xscape in Portland
room_description: Your team has been abducted by alien beings from an unknown planet. You wake up trapped inside a bizarre room where you are being held captive. Luckily the aliens have just left to go find some more humans to abduct before they leave our planet - you have 60 mins to try and escape before they return to their ship, leave earth and begin experimenting on you and your team!
